com.steelypip.powerups.hydraxml

Class HydraXMLWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.steelypip.powerups.hydraxml.ThemeableWriter<HydraXML>
      • com.steelypip.powerups.hydraxml.HydraXMLWriter

  • public class HydraXMLWriter
extends ThemeableWriter<HydraXML>
    Prints out a HydraXML object to a PrintWriter. It can be a simple-all-on-one-line or an elaborate pretty-printer depending on the Indenter, and look like XML or JSON depending on the Theme that is supplied.
